snippet.title: Kourtney Kardashian BEGS Scott Disick To Not Ruin Her Wedding With Travis Barker
snippet.description:
Kourtney Kardashian BEGS Scott Disick To Not Ruin Her Wedding With Travis Barker  
Kourtney Kardashian has now resorted to begging Scott Disick not to ruin her wedding with Travis Scott. This comes after Disick's extremely controversial comments regarding the upcoming wedding of Kourtney Kardashian. The news is also creating a buzz on social media as fans speculate whether Disick will go all the way and attempt to ruin the wedding plans of his ex-girlfriend. Although Travis Barker has not yet shown any intention of backing down from his wedding with Kourtney, Disick's reaction to the news might just be what pushes things over the edge. So, how has this love triangle developed lately, and what does it mean for the to-be-married couple? Let's find out in this video.
